text: Nancy Jones may refer to: * Nancy Jones, mother of rapper Jim Jones and cast member on Love & Hip Hop: New York and Chrissy & Mr. Jones. See List of Love & Hip Hop: New York cast members#Nancy "Mama" Jones. *Nancy Jones (missionary) (born 1860), an African-American missionary in Africa * Nancy Lane (née Jones), an Australian chess player See also: * Nancy Jones House
